Sinophil to hike capital to 20 bln pesos . Oil explorer Sinophil Corp said on Tuesday its board approved the increase in the company ' s authorised capital stock to 20 billion pesos from two billion . The board has also decided to change the par value of its shares to one peso from one centavo . A special stockholders ' meeting has been set on March 10 to take up the recommendations of its board , the company said . The company also said it has raised three billion pesos from a private placement to fund its planned investments for the year . Sinophil shares have been rising on the Philippine Stock Exchange on rumours it will be a holding company . - - Manila newsroom 632 841 - 8937 fax 8176267 
